dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents the major drainage systems within United States. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2. U.S. Drainage Systems (Generalized) provides a base map layer of major drainage systems of United States. ESRI. (2014). U.S. Drainage Systems (Generalized), 1990-1992. ESRI. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/dv507qz5701
